      </prefercite>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_cbb460c4c106a3c1e4ba41e4d9321370">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection cosists of correspondence; writings; teaching and casework material; typed manuscripts of her book, <title render="italic">Character Disorders in Parents of Delinquents</title>; notes and reference material (mostly printed) on adolescence, children, sex, and homosexuality; and a diary spanning the years 1969-72.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <userestrict id="aspace_f2596b9fda160e424389710a8be8c784">
